draw_text(info2_x, info2_y, "Ciuri Ciuri is a folk song from Sicily, composed by Francesco\nPaolo Frontini in 1883. It has been widely adapted over the\nyears, sung by a variety of different Italian artists. While\nthe name of the song means 'flowers' in Italian, the majority\nof the song is about a man unhappy with his wife who he\nfinds ugly and unpleasant.");